OL,4,CCroydon tram crash was fast and
OL,5,Cviolent, inquest told
OL,6, A reconstruction of a tram crash in
OL,7, Croydon that killed seven people has
OL,8, been shown to an inquest jury.
OL,10,FSimon French, chief inspector for the
OL,11,FRail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,12,F(RAIB), described the event of November
OL,13,F2016 as "fast and violent".
OL,15,FHe showed the court a video, first in
OL,16,Fslow motion and then at full speed, of
OL,17,Fa tram emerging from a tunnel at 78km/h
OL,18,F(48mph) before slowing down to 73km/h.
OL,20,FAs it reaches a bend, the tram starts
OL,21,Fto tip over and slides on its side.
